@startuml Sequence_UC22
title UC-22: Kelola Notifikasi

actor "Pengguna" as User
participant "Komponen Notifikasi\n(livewire/notification)" as View
participant "Notification\\Index\n(Livewire)" as Component
participant "Notification Model" as NotifModel
database "Database" as DB

User -> View: Klik ikon notifikasi
View -> Component: mount()
Component -> NotifModel: Notification::where('user_id',auth()->id())->latest()->get()
NotifModel -> DB: SELECT notifications WHERE user_id = ? ORDER BY created_at DESC
DB --> Component: Daftar notifikasi
Component --> View: Render daftar notifikasi (belum dibaca dibold)

== Baca Satu Notifikasi ==
User -> View: Klik salah satu notifikasi
View -> Component: markAsRead($notificationId)
Component -> NotifModel: Notification::find($id)->update(['is_read'=>true])
NotifModel -> DB: UPDATE notifications SET is_read = 1 WHERE id = ?
Component --> View: Perbarui tampilan notifikasi

== Tandai Semua Sudah Dibaca ==
User -> View: Klik "Tandai Semua Dibaca"
View -> Component: markAllAsRead()
Component -> NotifModel: Notification::where('user_id',auth()->id())->update(['is_read'=>true])
NotifModel -> DB: UPDATE notifications SET is_read = 1 WHERE user_id = ?
Component --> View: Semua notifikasi tampil sudah dibaca

@enduml
